797
00:52:59,000 --> 00:53:02,200
{\an8}<font color=#FF0000>...khozd-buzbi gimanim!</font>
<font color=#FFFF00>(...we've found the dwarf-maggot!)</font>

798
00:53:17,991 --> 00:53:19,617
Here, Mr. Gandalf...

799
00:53:19,618 --> 00:53:22,244
...can't you do something
about this deluge?

800
00:53:22,245 --> 00:53:24,872
It is raining, Master Dwarf...

801
00:53:24,873 --> 00:53:29,126
...and it will continue to rain
until the rain is done.

802
00:53:29,127 --> 00:53:30,836
If you wish to change...

803
00:53:30,837 --> 00:53:34,924
...the weather of the world,
find yourself another Wizard.

804
00:53:34,925 --> 00:53:36,383
- Are there any?
- What?

805
00:53:36,384 --> 00:53:39,136
- Other Wizards.
- There are five of us.

806
00:53:39,137 --> 00:53:43,849
The greatest of our order
is Saruman the White.

807
00:53:43,850 --> 00:53:47,603
Then there are the two Blue Wizards...

808
00:53:47,604 --> 00:53:51,148
Do you know,
I've quite forgotten their names.

809
00:53:51,149 --> 00:53:52,608
And who is the fifth?

810
00:53:52,609 --> 00:53:56,737
Well, that would be Radagast the Brown.

811
00:53:56,738 --> 00:54:01,738
Is he a great Wizard?
Or is he more like you?

812
00:54:02,536 --> 00:54:07,498
I think he's a very great Wizard,
in his own way.

813
00:54:07,499 --> 00:54:08,791
He's a gentle soul...

814
00:54:08,792 --> 00:54:12,211
...who prefers the company
of animals to others.

815
00:54:12,212 --> 00:54:15,464
He keeps a watchful eye
over the vast forest lands...

816
00:54:15,465 --> 00:54:18,175
<i>...to the east. And a good thing too.

817
00:54:18,176 --> 00:54:23,176
<i>For always evil will look to find
a foothold in this world.

818
00:54:29,688 --> 00:54:34,688
Not good. Not good at all.

819
00:54:40,365 --> 00:54:45,365
Eww.

820
00:54:57,007 --> 00:54:59,675
Oh, no. Sebastian.

821
00:55:03,054 --> 00:55:08,054
Good gracious.

822
00:55:25,160 --> 00:55:27,369
Come on. Move back! Give him some air...

823
00:55:27,370 --> 00:55:32,370
...for goodness sake.

824
00:55:39,215 --> 00:55:42,217
There. There.

825
00:55:42,218 --> 00:55:45,721
I don't understand why it's not working.

826
00:55:45,722 --> 00:55:50,517
It's not as if it's witchcraft.

827
00:55:50,518 --> 00:55:53,896
Witchcraft.

828
00:55:53,897 --> 00:55:58,897
Oh, but it is.

829
00:55:58,902 --> 00:56:03,902
A dark and powerful magic.

